<article><h1>Quiz maker with Multilingual Quiz Interface</h1><p class="date">Mon 14th Oct 2013<span class="f-right"><a href="index.html">&lt; Back to Blogs and Tutorials</a></span></p><div class="dotted"></div>ClassMarker will now be greeting test takers with a 'Hola', 'Bonjour' or 'Ni hao' among several different languages for members of our expanding international user base. <br />
<br />
We are proud to announce the release of a new multilingual student interface.<br />
<br />
<strong>Languages including:</strong><br />
Arabic<br />
Bulgarian<br />
Chinese (Simplified)<br />
Chinese (Traditional)<br />
Danish<br />
Dutch<br />
Finnish<br />
French<br />
German<br />
Greek<br />
Hungarian<br />
Italian<br />
Japanese<br />
Korean<br />
Malay<br />
Norwegian<br />
Polish<br />
Portuguese<br />
Romanian<br />
Russian<br />
Slovenian<br />
Spanish<br />
Swedish<br />
Turkish<br />
<br />
And plans to add more.<br />
<br />
<img class="img-shadow" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/img.classmarker.com/b/img/blog/language_quiz_maker.png" alt="Multilingual Quiz Interface"/><br />
Our new language option follows the successful launch of our upgraded <a href="https://www.classmarker.com/online-testing/blog/New-Quiz-Maker-Interface">online testing platform</a>  and has been seen as a 'must-have' for our growing international client-base. Quiz makers can now define their non-English speaking test takers' language settings so that they can take tests in their native tongues. The new feature means users are able to focus solely on their test questions without having to worry about correctly interpreting test instructions or buttons.<br />
<br />
The updated functionality has integrated seamlessly alongside ClassMarker's existing online settings features, which allow users to customize how students view and take their tests. To access our new languages feature, simply login to the ClassMarker's quiz maker and apply the language functionality via your Test Settings under the 'Advanced' option:<br />
<br />
<img class="img-shadow" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/img.classmarker.com/b/img/blog/language_selector.png" alt="Multilingual Quiz Interface selector"/><br />
Learn more about our multilingual test taker interface:<br />
<a href="../create-language-tests/index.html">Create online quizzes in multiple languages</a>.<br />
<br />
<br />
<a href="../../register/index.html">Register here</a> and start giving online exams today.<br />
<br />
